<codeline><highlight class="normal">See<sp/>&quot;Getting<sp/>Started&quot;<sp/>section<sp/>of<sp/>[EXAMPLES.MD](https://github.com/ocornut/imgui/blob/master/docs/EXAMPLES.md)<sp/>for<sp/>more<sp/>details.</highlight></codeline>
